{
  "name": "grow-app",
  "description": "SvelteKit/Svelte 5 site-mode HMI for a local hydroponic grow broker. The SvelteKit server keeps an MQTT session to a local Mosquitto broker, caches retained/current state, streams browser updates over SSE, and publishes commands only through discovered topics, with optional InfluxDB time-series history and its own local SQLite authentication. Note: this project has over 100 source files; consider scoping analysis to a subdirectory for faster results.",
